title: The Creek
description: In this Dateline classic, Danielle Locklear, a popular and charismatic high school freshman leaves home to drop off a notebook at her classmate’s house and never returns. Dennis Murphy reports. Originally aired on NBC on April 4, 2018.
author: nbcnews.podcasts@gmail.com (NBC News)
